          <physDesc>
            <p>Vellum, about 8 1/2 in. by 5 3/8, consisting of 104 leaves, some of which are much stained and torn, especially fol. 1, 2, 8, 28, 39, 47, 48, 55, 77, 78, 103 and 104. The quires are at present 11 in number, but ܗ, ܙ, ܚ, and ܛ have been lost, as well as several at the end. Leaves are also missing after foll. 79 and 84. What the original signatures of the quires were, does not appear; they are now signed with letters. There are from 18 to 21 lines in each page.</p>
            <objectDesc form="codex">
              <supportDesc material="perg">
                <support>
                  <material>Vellum</material>
                </support>
                <extent>
                  <measure type="composition" unit="leaf" quantity="104">104 ff.</measure>
                  <dimensions type="leaf" unit="in">
                    <height>
                      <measure type="height" quantity="8.5" unit="in">8 1/2</measure>
                    </height>
                    <width>
                      <measure type="width" quantity="5.375" unit="in">5 3/8</measure>
                    </width>
                  </dimensions>
                </extent>
                <foliation/>
                <collation>
                  <p>The quires are at present 11 in number.  What the original signatures of the quires were, does not appear.</p>
                </collation>
                <condition>
                  <p>Quires<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܚ</foreign>,<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܗ</foreign>,<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܙ</foreign>, and<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܛ</foreign>have been lost, as well as several at the end.</p>
                  <p>Some of the leaves are much stained and torn, especially fol.<locus>1</locus>,<locus>2</locus>,<locus>8</locus>,<locus>28</locus>,<locus>39</locus>,<locus>47</locus>,<locus>48</locus>,<locus>55</locus>,<locus>77</locus>,<locus>78</locus>,<locus>103</locus>and<locus>104</locus>.</p>
                  <p>Leaves are also missing after<locus>foll. 79</locus>and<locus>84</locus>
                  </p>
                </condition>
              </supportDesc>
              <layoutDesc>
                <layout columns="1" writtenLines="18 21">
                  <p>There are from 18 to 21 lines in each page.</p>
                </layout>
              </layoutDesc>
            </objectDesc>
