            <additions>
              <note type="proofreader-note">N.B., folio location may not be available for some items below.</note>
              <list>
                <item xml:id="addition1" n="1">
                  <p>Numerous Greek vowels have been added by a later hand (<foreign xml:lang="grc">α</foreign>,<foreign xml:lang="grc">ε</foreign>, ⲏ,<foreign xml:lang="grc">ω</foreign>,<foreign xml:lang="grc">ὄ</foreign>and<foreign xml:lang="grc">αυ</foreign>; e.g.<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܘܢܺܬܢܺܐܝܶܠ, ܘܐܘܨܡ, ܘܝܘܐܒ, ܝܬ, ܠܡ̇ܢܘ</foreign>).</p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition2" n="2">
                  <p>The same hand that added the vowel-points has divided the books into sections, marked by Greek letters on the margins. The last of these in 1 Chronicles is<foreign xml:lang="grc">ϊθ</foreign>(ch. xxii. 2), fol.<locus>48a</locus>; and in 2 Chronicles (commencing with<foreign xml:lang="grc">Δ</foreign>) ΚΓ (ch. xxix. 1), fol.<locus>104b</locus>.</p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition3" n="3">
                  <p>There are also a few marginal notes and glosses; e.g.</p>
                  <p>
                    <table>
                      <row>
                        <cell>fol.<locus from="3a" to="3a">3a</locus>,</cell>
                        <cell>
                          <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܘܐܺܘܝܡ,</foreign>,</cell>
                        <cell>marg.<foreign xml:lang="grc">ηαμ</foreign>
                        </cell>
                      </row>
                      <row>
                        <cell>fol.<locus from="11b" to="11b">11b</locus>,</cell>
                        <cell>
                          <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܣܩܐ̣</foreign>,</cell>
                        <cell>marg.<foreign xml:lang="grc">ⲤⲔⲰ</foreign>
                        </cell>
                      </row>
                      <row>
                        <cell>fol.<locus from="30a" to="30a">30a</locus>,</cell>
                        <cell>
                          <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܕܩܒܨܝܐܝܠ</foreign>,</cell>
                        <cell>marg.<foreign xml:lang="grc">ΚΑΒⲤΗΛ</foreign>
                        </cell>
                      </row>
                      <row>
                        <cell/>
                        <cell>
                          <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܢܘܠܐ ܕܓܪ̈ܕܚܐ</foreign>,</cell>
                        <cell>marg.<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܚܘ̈ܟܶܐ</foreign>
                        </cell>
                      </row>
                      <row>
                        <cell>fol.<locus from="36a" to="36a">36a</locus>,</cell>
                        <cell>
                          <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܘܕܒ̈ܠܐ. ܘܩܪ̈ܬܠܘܬܐ ܕܥ̈ܢܒܐ</foreign>(<ref target="#b1">1 Chron. xii. 40</ref>),</cell>
                        <cell>marg.<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܥ̈ܠܘܗܝ ܕܚܡܪܐ ܐܝܟ ܡܫܠܡܢܘܬܐ ܕܥܒܪ̈ܝܐ</foreign>and<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܪ̈ܠܝܬܐ ܕܥ̈ܢܒܐ</foreign>
                        </cell>
                      </row>
                    </table>
                  </p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition4" n="4">
                  <p>The quires are now signed with letters.</p>
                </item>
              </list>
            </additions>
